Every blog needs a first post, and what better subject to record than the birth of this blog.
Last weekend, I was reading a particular reddit post and noticed the OPs username forfunc. I&rsquo;ve also been watching (and loving!) @francesc&rsquo;s JustForFunc channel. I like the wordplay and thought myself very clever indeed when I came up with &ldquo;for func sake&rdquo;&hellip;
It just so happened that the username was available in the places I want to use it; and I&rsquo;ve been less than thrilled with my previous username choice(s)&hellip; so I spent an hour or so creating new accounts across the web.
